name: mapreduce.shuffle.max.connections
description:
Max allowed connections for the shuffle.  Set to 0 (zero)
               to indicate no limit on the number of connections.

name: ipc.client.kill.max
description: Defines the maximum number of clients to disconnect in one go.

name: dfs.client.deadnode.detection.probe.connection.timeout.ms
description: Connection timeout for probing dead node in milliseconds.

name: mapreduce.job.running.reduce.limit
description:
The maximum number of simultaneous reduce tasks per job.
  There is no limit if this value is 0 or negative.

name: fs.s3a.max.total.tasks
description:
The number of operations which can be queued for execution.
  This is in addition to the number of active threads in fs.s3a.threads.max.
